-B12A-BF20FA372322.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1065525" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/B20EEB7C-7813-4F9B-9905-20FFDC3BD271-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/B20EEB7C-7813-4F9B-9905-20FFDC3BD271-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/B20EEB7C-7813-4F9B-9905-20FFDC3BD271-1280x720.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/B20EEB7C-7813-4F9B-9905-20FFDC3BD271-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/B20EEB7C-7813-4F9B-9905-20FFDC3BD271-1536x864.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/B20EEB7C-7813-4F9B-9905-20FFDC3BD271.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">原先有傳言指出，新一代 Airpods 會與上個月發佈的 iPhone 13 系列和 Apple Watch 一同發佈，但發佈會中卻未能看到它的身影。有消息指，新一代 AirPods 將仿效 AirPods Pro 的外型，不過可能沿用 AirPods 無耳塞的設計，耳機柄也將短於 AirPods Pro，且不具備降噪功能，價錢方面應相對較平。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1065526" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/ED275450-6BAD-4F08-856F-55AC81A675E4-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/ED275450-6BAD-4F08-856F-55AC81A675E4-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/ED275450-6BAD-4F08-856F-55AC81A675E4-1280x720.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/ED275450-6BAD-4F08-856F-55AC81A675E4-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/ED275450-6BAD-4F08-856F-55AC81A675E4-1536x864.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/ED275450-6BAD-4F08-856F-55AC81A675E4.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">另外，有報道指 Apple 將推出 M1X 晶片的 14、16 吋 MacBook Pro 和 Mac mini。配備 M1X 晶片的 14 吋、16 吋 MacBook Pro 機型，重點在其更高效能的 M1X 晶片，傳具備 8 個效能核心及 2 個節能核心，16 或 32 核心的 GPU，支援最高可擴充到 64GB RAM，而現今 M1 晶片的 MacBook Pro 為 16GB；至於連接埠也傳出將改回多種接口，包括 MagSafe 充電、HDMI、SD 讀卡機等，可能移除 Touch Bar 改為傳統的實體功能按鍵。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1065528" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/37569F35-73F1-40E3-A0E8-93D0012145A8-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/37569F35-73F1-40E3-A0E8-93D0012145A8-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/37569F35-73F1-40E3-A0E8-93D0012145A8-1280x720.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/37569F35-73F1-40E3-A0E8-93D0012145A8-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/37569F35-73F1-40E3-A0E8-93D0012145A8-1536x864.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/37569F35-73F1-40E3-A0E8-93D0012145A8-2048x1152.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/37569F35-73F1-40E3-A0E8-93D0012145A8.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">而 M1X 晶片的 Mac mini 主機也有望同步推出。有爆料者稱機殼有望全新設計，頂部將採用類有機玻璃材質，搭配鋁製機身外殼，並且具有更多的連接埠，包括 4 個 Tunderbolt 3、兩個 USB、乙太網路埠和 HDMI，以及像是今年 24 吋 M1 晶片 iMac 的磁吸充電連接線。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源： <a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2021/10/13/new-airpods-during-unleashed-apple-event/">Macrumors</a></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 : </span><a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
